---
---

<section id="comparison" class="py-[7.5rem] bg-[#0A0A0A] relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.025]"
    style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 30%, #ff3333 0%, transparent 55%);">
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
      <div class="section-label mb-6" style="border-color: rgba(255,68,68,0.35); color: #ff6666;">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500 animate-pulse inline-block"></span>
        The Pain
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black tracking-tight text-balance">
        3 Silent Killers <span class="text-white/35">Draining Your Revenue Right Now</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-white/50 mt-5 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto">
        These aren't hypothetical risks. They're happening every single day you operate without autonomous AI infrastructure.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Silent Killers Stack -->
    <div class="space-y-5">

      <!-- Killer 1: Traffic Leakage -->
      <div class="killer-card relative rounded-sm border border-red-500/20 bg-red-950/10 p-5 sm:p-8 md:p-10 overflow-hidden group transition-all duration-300 hover:border-red-500/40">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-72 h-72 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700 pointer-events-none"
          style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,50,50,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%);">
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start gap-8">
          <!-- Icon -->
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-sm bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/25 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#ff5555" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M3 3l18 18"/>
                <path d="M10.5 6H19v8.5"/>
                <path d="M5 12c0 3.87 3.13 7 7 7s7-3.13 7-7"/>
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1" fill="#ff5555"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Content -->
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="text-xs text-red-400/60 font-mono uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Silent Killer #01</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black mb-1 text-white">Traffic Leakage</h3>
            <div class="text-red-400/80 text-sm font-semibold mb-5">— The Hole in the Bucket</div>
            <p class="text-white/50 text-base leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-7">
              You're paying for clicks, attention, and intent — then watching 63% of those visitors evaporate before a single human can respond.
              Your funnel isn't a funnel. It's a sieve. Every ad dollar spent without instant AI engagement is <span class="text-white font-semibold">63 cents poured directly into the void.</span>
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
              <div class="bg-[#0A0A0A] border border-red-500/10 rounded-sm p-4">
                <div class="text-2xl font-black text-red-400 tabular-nums">63%</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-white/30 mt-1 leading-snug">of leads never convert to even a conversation</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-[#0A0A0A] border border-red-500/10 rounded-sm p-4">
                <div class="text-2xl font-black text-red-400 tabular-nums">5 min</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-white/30 mt-1 leading-snug">before a warm lead goes permanently cold</div>
              </div>
              <div class="hidden md:block bg-[#0A0A0A] border border-red-500/10 rounded-sm p-4">
                <div class="text-2xl font-black text-red-400 tabular-nums">$0</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-white/30 mt-1 leading-snug">recovered from leaked traffic without automation</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Killer 2: Manual Work Trap -->
      <div class="killer-card relative rounded-sm border border-orange-500/20 bg-orange-950/10 p-5 sm:p-8 md:p-10 overflow-hidden group transition-all duration-300 hover:border-orange-500/40">
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-72 h-72 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700 pointer-events-none"
          style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,140,50,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%);">
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start gap-8">
          <!-- Icon -->
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-sm bg-orange-500/10 border border-orange-500/25 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f97316" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M12 2v20M2 12h20"/>
                <path d="M12 7a5 5 0 0 1 5 5"/>
                <path d="M12 17a5 5 0 0 1-5-5"/>
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3" stroke="#f97316" stroke-width="2"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Content -->
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="text-xs text-orange-400/60 font-mono uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Silent Killer #02</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black mb-1 text-white">The Manual Work Trap</h3>
            <div class="text-orange-400/80 text-sm font-semibold mb-5">— Work a System Should Be Doing</div>
            <p class="text-white/50 text-base leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-7">
              Your team is spending 4–6 hours a day on follow-ups, scheduling, qualifying calls, and chasing cold leads.
              You're paying <span class="text-white font-semibold">human-rate wages for robotic-rate tasks</span> — work that an AI system handles in milliseconds, with perfect consistency, 24 hours a day.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
              <div class="bg-[#0A0A0A] border border-orange-500/10 rounded-sm p-4">
                <div class="text-2xl font-black text-orange-400 tabular-nums">4–6 hrs</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-white/30 mt-1 leading-snug">wasted daily on work AI handles instantly</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-[#0A0A0A] border border-orange-500/10 rounded-sm p-4">
                <div class="text-2xl font-black text-orange-400 tabular-nums">87%</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-white/30 mt-1 leading-snug">of leads never receive a second follow-up touch</div>
              </div>
              <div class="hidden md:block bg-[#0A0A0A] border border-orange-500/10 rounded-sm p-4">
                <div class="text-2xl font-black text-orange-400 tabular-nums">$12K+</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-white/30 mt-1 leading-snug">monthly in rep cost doing automatable work</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Killer 3: Lost Revenue Ghost -->
      <div class="killer-card relative rounded-sm border border-red-500/20 bg-red-950/10 p-5 sm:p-8 md:p-10 overflow-hidden group transition-all duration-300 hover:border-red-500/40">
        <div class="absolute top-1/2 right-0 -translate-y-1/2 w-72 h-72 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700 pointer-events-none"
          style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,50,50,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%);">
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start gap-8">
          <!-- Icon -->
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-sm bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/25 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#ff5555" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M12 2C8 2 5 5.5 5 9c0 5 7 13 7 13s7-8 7-13c0-3.5-3-7-7-7z"/>
                <path d="M12 11.5a2.5 2.5 0 1 0 0-5 2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0 5z"/>
                <path d="M8 20l-2 2M16 20l2 2" stroke-opacity="0.4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Content -->
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="text-xs text-red-400/60 font-mono uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Silent Killer #03</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black mb-1 text-white">The Lost Revenue Ghost</h3>
            <div class="text-red-400/80 text-sm font-semibold mb-5">— The Money You Don't See Leaving</div>
            <p class="text-white/50 text-base leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-7">
              This isn't hypothetical. It's the compound cost of slow responses, missed follow-ups, and unqualified calls that disguise themselves as "just a slow month."
              <span class="text-white font-semibold">$25,000+ is leaving your business every month.</span> Silently. Invisibly. And without a system to stop it, it always will.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
              <div class="bg-[#0A0A0A] border border-red-500/10 rounded-sm p-4">
                <div class="text-2xl font-black text-red-400 tabular-nums">$25K+</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-white/30 mt-1 leading-snug">leaking from your pipeline every single month</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-[#0A0A0A] border border-red-500/10 rounded-sm p-4">
                <div class="text-2xl font-black text-red-400 tabular-nums">Invisible</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-white/30 mt-1 leading-snug">doesn't show on your P&L — disguised as "slow months"</div>
              </div>
              <div class="hidden md:block bg-[#0A0A0A] border border-red-500/10 rounded-sm p-4">
                <div class="text-2xl font-black text-red-400 tabular-nums">Compounding</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-white/30 mt-1 leading-snug">every unconverted lead is a lost referral chain too</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Bottom CTA pull -->
    <div class="text-center mt-16">
      <p class="text-white/40 text-base mb-6">
        Every month you wait is another <span class="text-white font-semibold">$25,000+</span> your pipeline doesn't capture.
      </p>
      <a href="#diagnostic" class="neon-btn inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 text-sm font-bold rounded-sm">
        Run My Revenue Audit
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3">
          <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
